node.text:
Trophy hunter carries leopard kill! PLEASE CLICK THE LINK IN OUR BIO FOR MORE INFORMATION @animalonplanet🙏😓
-
Trophy hunting is hunting of wild animals as trophies, with the whole or parts of the animal kept as a trophy as a reminder of the kill. The pictures above show distressing pain these animals go through.
-
+125,000 animals are brutally killed each year by trophy hunters. This cruel sport is pushing species to the brink of extinction. The aim of hunters is to kill animals with superior  genetic characteristics, which is the animal that contributes to the adaptation and survival of the species. (link in bio to support and end this @animalonplanet ) 🤏

We are raising money from each t-shirt sold and donating to charities that oppose trophy  hunting, to help keep their campaigns running and get us closer to this horror ending. These charities work continuously with an effort to end this!
-
LINK IN BIO TO HELP END TROPHY HUNTING🙏😓❤️( @animalonplanet 🤏🤏🤏)
